dence and a sense of purpose in voting.</p><p class="a">It is with great pleasure, again, that I just offer our support and, also, thanks for the opportunity to provide feedback through this process, which our co-leader Metiria Turei did. So, again, the Green Party supports these nominations.</p></div></body>
