							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="VoteReason">A party vote was called for on the question,<em> That the </em><em>Education Legislation Bill be now read a third time.</em></p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Ayes 63</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand National 59; Māori Party 2; ACT New Zealand 1; United Future 1.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Noes 55</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand Labour 29; Green Party 14; New Zealand First 12.</p><p class="VoteResult">Bill read a third time.</p></div></body>
